1
00:00:14,725 --> 00:00:18,487
♪Allergic to fast-food love,
even if it's too naive♪

2
00:00:18,562 --> 00:00:22,162
♪Just like a hug needs
the right body heat♪

3
00:00:22,287 --> 00:00:25,437
♪Your "same here" carries
a touch of resolve♪

4
00:00:25,862 --> 00:00:29,412
♪Pack my bags, we can set off right now♪

5
00:00:29,637 --> 00:00:33,112
♪The future is a wondrous,
unknown adventure♪

6
00:00:33,250 --> 00:00:36,712
♪The journey itself is what
truly matters before the destination♪

7
00:00:36,787 --> 00:00:40,975
♪Those moments together
are what bind us strongest♪

8
00:00:41,025 --> 00:00:42,612
♪Connect♪

9
00:00:42,625 --> 00:00:43,275
♪Let's go!♪

10
00:00:43,612 --> 00:00:47,137
♪Leave worries behind
in yesterday's sentimentality♪

11
00:00:47,237 --> 00:00:50,675
♪Today, no dwelling
on negative emotions♪

12
00:00:50,750 --> 00:00:53,450
♪Tomorrow holds more luck♪

13
00:00:53,450 --> 00:00:55,262
♪Together we'll create moving melodies♪

14
00:00:55,262 --> 00:00:58,199
♪The future begins to take shape♪

15
00:00:59,075 --> 00:01:02,375
=Love In A Secret=
(I Just Want to Drown With You)

16
00:01:02,675 --> 00:01:06,262
=Episode 6=

17
00:01:31,737 --> 00:01:33,217
Ye Man.

18
00:01:33,217 --> 00:01:35,617
Hello, Ms. Huang?

19
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:45,240
Wake up.

20
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:48,280
You're back.

21
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:53,080
Why did he drink so much?

22
00:01:58,320 --> 00:01:59,120
Lu.

23
00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:01,840
I will treat you

24
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:03,640
as my biological daughter.

25
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:06,840
Can you please forgive me

26
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:09,280
for what I've done wrong before this?

27
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:22,720
How are you so bad at this when you've
been learning since you were 12?

28
00:02:22,720 --> 00:02:23,720
What has that got to do with you?

29
00:02:23,720 --> 00:02:25,280
I suppose it was a different person.

30
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,760
Listen up.

31
00:02:27,760 --> 00:02:29,180
You'd better mind your own business.

32
00:02:31,040 --> 00:02:32,160
Alright now.

33
00:02:32,160 --> 00:02:33,862
I just want to apologize to you.

34
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:37,080
I was drunk last night.

35
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:40,040
What kind of apology is that?

36
00:02:40,040 --> 00:02:41,825
Is being drunk even an excuse?

37
00:02:41,825 --> 00:02:43,950
How could you fall for everyone you see?

38
00:02:43,950 --> 00:02:44,950
I didn't.

39
00:02:44,950 --> 00:02:46,560
You're truly interesting.

40
00:02:47,100 --> 00:02:49,462
I can never tell
when you're speaking the truth.

41
00:02:53,937 --> 00:02:55,537
Why are you following me?

42
00:02:55,537 --> 00:02:57,257
I'll do whatever you do.

43
00:03:08,362 --> 00:03:09,242
Hello, Qun?

44
00:03:11,212 --> 00:03:12,412
Who's back?

45
00:03:13,450 --> 00:03:14,250
Where is he?

46
00:03:15,700 --> 00:03:18,140
Boss, I know my fault.

47
00:03:18,275 --> 00:03:19,275
I won't do it again.

48
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:22,160
Boss!

49
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:23,520
What are you doing?

50
00:03:24,375 --> 00:03:25,412
Zhu?

51
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,640
Hi, Miss Lu.

52
00:03:31,440 --> 00:03:33,520
Zhu, you're finally here.

53
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:35,040
Look, I was punched.

54
00:03:35,640 --> 00:03:37,240
With a wound like that,

55
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:39,440
I suppose it'll heal up
if I come an hour later.

56
00:03:41,200 --> 00:03:42,840
Long time no see. Give me a hug.

57
00:03:43,937 --> 00:03:45,937
It's been so long since you came back,

58
00:03:45,940 --> 00:03:47,440
yet you got yourself into
a fight right away.

59
00:03:47,440 --> 00:03:48,680
Does your father know about this?

60
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:51,280
Who told him to steal from my factory?

61
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:53,120
I'm punishing the wicked
and rewarding the good.

62
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:54,440
If you do this again,

63
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:56,680
I'll chop off your arm. You hear me?

64
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:00,080
Come with me.

65
00:04:05,200 --> 00:04:06,800
How long will you be staying this time?

66
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:10,600
Of course it's until the time
you no longer wish to see me.

67
00:04:10,600 --> 00:04:11,787
You should leave, then.

68
00:04:13,160 --> 00:04:14,440
Miss Lu,

69
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:17,680
can you please not be this cold to me?

70
00:04:17,825 --> 00:04:19,345
You weren't like this before.

71
00:04:21,760 --> 00:04:23,200
I was just joking.

72
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:24,400
I'll buy you a meal.

73
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:26,600
Come on. What do you want to eat?

74
00:04:27,675 --> 00:04:30,960
Of course I wish to have
your home-cooked food.

75
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:32,520
Mind your words.

76
00:04:35,762 --> 00:04:37,800
I heard that your father
got you a stepmother.

77
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:39,600
And, your stepmother
got you a stepbrother.

78
00:04:40,960 --> 00:04:42,360
How did you know?

79
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:43,520
But of course.

80
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:44,720
As long as it's related to you,

81
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:47,200
I'll use all of my connections
to get to the bottom of it.

82
00:04:47,200 --> 00:04:48,560
Why did you think I was in such a hurry

83
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:49,920
when my father told me to come back?

84
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:51,080
I just want to see you.

85
00:04:52,520 --> 00:04:53,200
By the way,

86
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:54,600
how's that stepbrother of yours?

87
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:58,920
He's nothing special.

88
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:01,135
He's very ordinary.

89
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:02,625
Is that so?

90
00:05:02,687 --> 00:05:03,967
If he dares to bully you,

91
00:05:03,967 --> 00:05:05,487
I'll teach him a lesson.

92
00:05:05,825 --> 00:05:07,105
Go on, then.

93
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:17,960
Don't tell me he's your stepbrother.

94
00:05:27,250 --> 00:05:28,787
Do your friends only consist of thugs?

95
00:05:28,840 --> 00:05:30,440
Who are you calling a thug?

96
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:33,240
Come with me.

97
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:34,440
She's not going with you.

98
00:05:34,440 --> 00:05:35,080
Let me explain.

99
00:05:35,080 --> 00:05:36,510
She's not listening to your explanation.

100
00:05:36,525 --> 00:05:38,840
You're so irritating.

101
00:05:44,440 --> 00:05:47,400
So, you're Ye Man,
the top student who just came back

102
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:48,360
from the US, right?

103
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:50,160
Listen up.

104
00:05:50,160 --> 00:05:52,000
I'm Chen Tianze.

105
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:54,600
Hai City is my territory.

106
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:57,400
Lu Zhu is under my protection as well.

107
00:05:57,400 --> 00:05:58,320
Do not bully her.

108
00:05:58,320 --> 00:05:59,160
You hear me?

109
00:05:59,160 --> 00:06:00,600
Come home with me right now.

110
00:06:04,350 --> 00:06:06,070
Did I say I was going to leave with you?

111
00:06:06,080 --> 00:06:07,805
Did she say she was
going to leave with you?

112
00:06:07,805 --> 00:06:09,725
Why are you trying to drag her home?

113
00:06:09,725 --> 00:06:11,990
I don't understand what you two
are talking about at all.

114
00:06:15,700 --> 00:06:17,300
You can choose to stay here

115
00:06:17,300 --> 00:06:18,540
if you want to see me

116
00:06:19,300 --> 00:06:20,990
turn this dumb friend of yours
into a complete idiot.

117
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:23,720
Come back!

118
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:24,875
My car!

119
00:06:24,875 --> 00:06:25,760
Ye Man?

120
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:36,640
What do you mean by this?

121
00:06:46,760 --> 00:06:48,800
Don't worry. He can't leave.

122
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:50,160
He can't just run me over.

123
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:53,960
Are you actually doing it?

124
00:06:57,487 --> 00:06:59,047
Deliver her car to our house later.

125
00:06:59,812 --> 00:07:01,080
Ye Man, come back!

126
00:07:03,320 --> 00:07:04,920
Boss, should we deliver her car?

127
00:07:05,012 --> 00:07:06,812
Darn it.

128
00:07:06,812 --> 00:07:08,362
Why should I listen to him?

129
00:07:13,237 --> 00:07:15,717
Deliver the car to her, you idiot!

130
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:18,440
Where is he?

131
00:07:18,440 --> 00:07:19,160
Bring him here.

132
00:07:24,200 --> 00:07:25,480
Relay my message to your boss.

133
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:26,400
Tell him that I'm back.

134
00:07:26,400 --> 00:07:27,720
Bring him to me.

135
00:07:28,520 --> 00:07:29,560
And,

136
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:31,320
I'm the one in charge of the racetrack.

137
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:32,320
You hear me?

138
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:39,912
Can you hear me out now?

139
00:07:39,912 --> 00:07:40,992
It's pointless.

140
00:07:40,992 --> 00:07:42,700
Whatever you do
has nothing to do with me.

141
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,200
Who said so?

142
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:07,640
I don't know why either.

143
00:08:07,737 --> 00:08:09,017
I was always a composed person.

144
00:08:09,017 --> 00:08:10,040
But when I saw you last night,

145
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:11,087
and after I drank...

146
00:08:11,125 --> 00:08:12,440
So, whatever you did doesn't count

147
00:08:12,440 --> 00:08:14,200
because you got drunk last night,

148
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:16,480
right?

149
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:30,880
Lu!

150
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:40,080
Listen.

151
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:43,280
I didn't approach you on purpose.

152
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:46,240
I don't intend to use you either.

153
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:48,880
I'm not deceiving you.

154
00:08:49,760 --> 00:08:50,560
And,

155
00:08:55,560 --> 00:08:56,360
I...

156
00:08:56,900 --> 00:09:01,400
♪Bit by bit, I'll forget you♪

157
00:09:01,625 --> 00:09:05,413
♪Bit by bit, I'll erase the memories♪

158
00:09:05,588 --> 00:09:09,663
♪From now on,
your image won't linger in my mind♪

159
00:09:09,663 --> 00:09:13,800
♪Nor will those fragments of the past♪

160
00:09:13,925 --> 00:09:17,700
♪Days will slowly drift away
like passing clouds♪

161
00:09:17,700 --> 00:09:21,475
♪I'll learn to stop
longing for what's gone♪

162
00:09:21,475 --> 00:09:23,750
♪The you in my memories♪

163
00:09:23,750 --> 00:09:25,763
♪Will fade from clarity♪

164
00:09:25,763 --> 00:09:29,062
♪How much longer must I wait to♪

165
00:09:29,350 --> 00:09:33,562
♪Forget you completely♪

166
00:09:35,040 --> 00:09:36,440
I don't know what to do either.

167
00:09:37,920 --> 00:09:40,200
But I think I fell for
my younger sister.

168
00:09:46,800 --> 00:09:48,200
I'll just take that as nonsense.

169
00:09:53,040 --> 00:09:54,050
I'll head home first.

170
00:09:54,112 --> 00:09:57,737
♪Days will slowly drift away
like passing clouds♪

171
